Individual




Sujeet Chand



Dr. Sujeet Chand is Chief Technology Officer & Senior Vice President at Rockwell Automation, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Wisconsin Technology Council.
Dr. Chand was previously employed as a Director, Manager & Principal Scientist by Rockwell Scientific Co. LLC. He also served on the board at University of Wisconsin Foundation.
He received his graduate degree from the University of Florida and a doctorate degree from the University of Florida.



